www-jrd - jrd website

directory structure:

  css                - css files
  f                  - html files (GENERATED)
  f/db               - flickr database files (GENERATED)
  haskell            - haskell source code
  haskell/Flickr.hs  - minimal flickr api bindings
  haskell/jrd-f.hs   - code to generate site proper (f/)
  haskell/jrd-a.hs   - code to generate archive list (f/a/)

requirements:

  ghc                - http://haskell.org/ghc/
  html-minimalist    - darcs get http://slavepianos.org/rd/sw/html-minimalist
  xml                - git clone git://code.galois.com/xml.git
  tagsoup            - darcs get http://www.cs.york.ac.uk/fp/darcs/tagsoup
